randoop - Randoop Unit Test Generator

USAGE:
    randoop <command> [options...]

DESCRIPTION:
    Generate unit tests using Randoop tool. Supports test generation,
    minimization, and help commands.

COMMANDS:
    gen <class-name>
        Generate tests for specified class

    help
        Show Randoop help

ARGUMENTS:
    class-name
        Fully qualified class name or Java file path

CONFIGURATION:
    -conf-dev-randoop-heap OPTIONS
        JVM heap options for Randoop

    -conf-dev-randoop-options OPTIONS
        Default Randoop options

EXAMPLES:
    randoop gen com.example.MyClass
    randoop gen src/main/java/com/example/MyClass.java
    randoop help
